            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>curry powder </strong>with<strong> half</strong> your <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>(you'll use the rest for later!)<strong> </strong>in a medium bowl</p><p>Add the <strong>chicken thighs </strong>and <strong>sliced pepper </strong>to the bowl with<strong> </strong>a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
