        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>coated chicken thighs </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 17-18 min or until the pepper is slightly charred and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) - this is your <strong>tandoori chicken thighs</strong></p>",
